So I swim across the lake, and see a group killing Deep Water Goblins, about 5 of 'em. <br>
&quot;Hail! Fellow Rogue!&quot;<br>
&quot;Sup?&quot;<br>
&quot;Can any of you cast Invis vs Undead?&quot;<br>
&quot;Nope sorry, why?&quot;<br>
&quot;Well.... I kinda climbed up the ladder in the tower on the island... and died.&quot;<br>
