<br>
You *do* know that hidden rogues are automatically invisible to undead as well as regular mobs, right?  There are some creatures that can still see us, and sometimes a creature that normally can't see us will catch a glimpse and attack.  But for the most part, your sneak/hide will work just as well against undead as the living.<br>
<br>
I've heard debates about spectres.  In my experience they can't see us, but I might have just gotten lucky.<br>
<br>
